\par }{\b\fs32\cf1 \hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0 NOTES.}{\fs32\cf1 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0 In some ways, the Booster League is a good way to teach a *group* of people how to play On the Edge (whereas the Omni League is a good way to teach an individual). Trading helps people learn the relative (and su
\hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0 bjective) values of cards and gives them enough cards to try different deck-building strategies. 
\par 
